headline: U.S. Bank personal loans now available through State Farm®
summary: MINNEAPOLIS, March 26, 2025--In the latest expansion of the State Farm and U.S. Bank alliance, State Farm customers can now apply for U.S. Bank personal loans for up to $50,000 working directly with their agent. The new offering joins the existing suite of U.S. Bank products accessible through State Farm agents that includes deposits, co-branded credit cards and a full suite of business banking products and services.
